{"tid":1747151,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒：用選票證明港人冇割席","createTime":"2019-11-23T05:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T00:44:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":108,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"3150f088f6adbc26111568644ac90b7dd802704e","tid":1747151,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:50:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/UMNXYB3XDC54C33I2UPPM6EBYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2FUMNXYB3XDC54C33I2UPPM6EBYQ%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=10ef032c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2FUMNXYB3XDC54C33I2UPPM6EBYQ%2F&h=5d35eba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/UMNXYB3XDC54C33I2UPPM6EBYQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒：用選票證明港人冇割席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191123/large/1574440455_90ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191123%2Flarge%2F1574440455_90ee.jpg&h=c6e88111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒指若民主派在區會奪過半議席，可令抗爭運動有更大民意支持。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次區選唯一因為政治原因被DQ的香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒指，明日的區選結果不但對國際社會理解香港反修例運動起關鍵作用，民主派的得票亦可以證明「香港人從來冇割席」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱有助國際理解抗爭運動<br />\n<br />\n報名循南區海怡西參選的黃之鋒，上月底被選舉主任蔡亮以非真心摒棄「港獨」作為自決前途的選項為理由，DQ其參選資格，成為今次區選唯一因為政治原因被DQ的參選人。將香港問題帶上國際社會的黃指，國際社會非常重視今次投票結果：「如果民主派嘅總得票係過百萬，甚至比建制派嘅得票多好多，係對國際社會理解香港嘅運動好關鍵。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充，國際社會過去一個月多次提出質疑，認為運動不斷升級或會令民意逆轉，但他並不認同，「（要）透過大家嘅選票讓全世界知道，面對中大守護戰，面對（有人在）警署（疑遭）輪姦，面對黑警暴力之後，香港人從來冇割席」。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒指出，若然民主派可以在區議會452席的民選議席中過半，可以令整場抗爭運動有更大的民意支持，同時若每個選區都有願意守護社區的代議士，對前線抗爭者亦是重要的支持。他表示，政府會否突然腰斬選舉仍是未知之數，故呼籲民主派支持者明日盡早投票，指越早投票越能證明抗爭者的意志，亦說明市民不會縱容政府取消選舉。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"b97350cbaaadce92ae258b0d51540626124407a3","tid":1747151,"uid":156096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先75%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=b720e29e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fn&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=d6c89ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/n</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期日0730 見)"},{"pid":"31e0eeff712f42244fd9523488ef203b645bb1c1","tid":1747151,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"DQ 師"},{"pid":"b4d074ddb435bde88c896dc80156cb229d1aa9f3","tid":1747151,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"迫害體驗師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb140741b1758e1a56b5d5f53a915b7f0c31d621","tid":1747151,"uid":37413,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"團結啲香港人，到呢個時侯我哋冇本錢分化<br />\n由頭到尾輸到仆街冇贏過，諗吓我哋犧牲咗幾多手足，生嘅傷、死嘅死唔眼閉、比人姦、坐十年冇前途，佢哋為咗咩？<br />\n團結一次贏一次得唔得"},{"pid":"8fe8971af0e65c52b5a1e835e36e5989409b01ab","tid":1747151,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>顯嘉請集中投5號</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/895184207211734/permalink/2692521227478014?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F895184207211734%2Fpermalink%2F2692521227478014%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=8060498c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/895184207211734/permalink/2692521227478014?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8c2909e6d7662b8dae8fa80cce7ae6f793da0da1","tid":1747151,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"票一定要投<br />\n<br />\n但唔當個% 係民意<br />\n<br />\n建制種票，我地贏極可能都係50 / 50"},{"pid":"2cd3d04d34cd5e67dfbce51289714557ad3f6bc5","tid":1747151,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:48:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b56b54685a6da01293e04fbb7d1cd19e8ce8b205","tid":1747151,"uid":214173,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"預演<br />\n林鄭:今屆區議會選舉有超過6成選民投票支持建制派議員,民意上支持