「如果民主派嘅總得票係過百萬，甚至比建制派嘅得票多好多，係對國際社會理解香港嘅運動好關鍵。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充，國際社會過去一個月多次提出質疑，認為運動不斷升級或會令民意逆轉，但他並不認同，「（要）透過大家嘅選票讓全世界知道，面對中大守護戰，面對（有人在）警署（疑遭）輪姦，面對黑警暴力之後，香港人從來冇割席」。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒指出，若然民主派可以在區議會452席的民選議席中過半，可以令整場抗爭運動有更大的民意支持，同時若每個選區都有願意守護社區的代議士，對前線抗爭者亦是重要的支持。他表示，政府會否突然腰斬選舉仍是未知之數，故呼籲民主派支持者明日盡早投票，指越早投票越能證明抗爭者的意志，亦說明市民不會縱容政府取消選舉。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"區選此局獲勝關鍵只有 &lsquo;避免輸左帶嚟嘅惡果&rsquo;。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezFsGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezFsGS</a>"},{"pid":"236590e841d01f25b3909963db272efb6ac7be76","tid":1747151,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2909e6d7662b8dae8fa80cce7ae6f793da0da1","tid":1747151,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"票一定要投<br />\n<br />\n但唔當個% 係民意<br />\n<br />\n建制種票，我地贏極可能都係50 / 50"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"講票數啊,關種票咩事,種票只係拎個人去第二度投,都係得一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c0dc771c25ad8caa1e571db0886b2ec271616a","tid":1747151,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19dc19f8985b8577115f6fb975869866809de30","tid":1747151,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"肥左咁多既<br />\n個肚腩走左出黎<br />\n<br />\n十卜gphone"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"張秀賢都係"},{"pid":"5d975cb45f1d1961436246d4d4a5dde9ce5237bf","tid":1747151,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5399687859b9c8248d53b60ed77f48724059e88c","tid":1747151,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8yQUK2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8yQUK2.png&h=727d0b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、民主派議員、及候選人<br />\n<br />\n等候時及面對<span style=\"color: red;\">白警</span>時唱<strong>《Sing Hallelujah To The Lord》</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港區 6:00pm 灣仔紅隧入口集合，大量兩層巴士接過紅隧，或自行行過紅隧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致 撞區候選人，<br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>申請不反通知書，否則只有零票。</span></span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpIeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=12e25938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a>"},{"pid":"7c32d6cf8f2e1cc378544ef024889686a8839c43","tid":1747151,"uid":13594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792157656fee221978c3f3e787ec30ae01ccae3f","tid":1747151,"uid":216564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"1124齊投票 光復香港時代革命！區議會選舉集中討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b401e3ae1e07c69b84a2f50c7eb1c7472ea53ca4","tid":1747151,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:59:31.000Z","msg":"一定要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff6ecadb73e3687d82dfc1a060a8ad685c990a0","tid":1747151,"uid":56326,"like":0,"disli